# Factorio Master Class

These blueprints are taken from [Factorio Master Class](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLV3rF--heRVu2xlDGZiRbdb7nbwzM9Vyz), an excellent Youtube series done by [Nilaus](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCD80bzqJh1N7lOqn7n0vKTg).

## Jump Start 0.18 by Nilaus

[A structured 'first base'](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cx88mE-4P4Y&list=PLV3rF--heRVu2xlDGZiRbdb7nbwzM9Vyz&index=2) that you will build when you start playing Factorio. Good for completing all red and green science technology.

## Vanilla Train Network by Haphollas

More of a mid/late game nice to have, [a pure vanilla approach](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4VgZv35yUI) for scheduling trains to and from stations.

```text

```

Train Schedule:
- DEPOT: `15s` passed AND Circuit `resource` >= 1
- `resource` LOAD: Full cargo inventory AND Circuit `green` > 0
- `resource` UNLOAD: Empty cargo inventory OR `5s` inactivity
